<h1>üßò 15-Minute Rest Day Routine</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Mobility, stretching & light core work for recovery</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <strong>When to use:</strong> Days 3, 6, 7 of your training week<br>
  <strong>Goal:</strong> Improve mobility, blood flow, and recovery ‚Äî NOT to build muscle<br>
  <strong>Intensity:</strong> Easy. If it feels like a workout, you're going too hard.
</div>

